# Infrastructure

- Local dev: `infra/docker/docker-compose.yml` (SDD §21).
- Production: Kubernetes via Helm; cloud resources via Terraform (Phase 4).
- Secrets never committed — use env vars or secret stores.
- Pin image and provider versions in IaC files.
